82,-0.03540153,-0.00070212,-0.0278213,0.01852316,-0.0048464,0.20193508,-0.05692161,0.09818423,0.00877805,0.04184143,0.0217829,0.05317853,-0.0604609,-0.02862985,-0.04110675,0.12524799,-0.06885061,-0.01035666,0.03437403,0.00523985,-0.00533115,-0.02168984,0.04262305,-0.04648931,-0.04018459,0.01057307,0.04326803,0.12739016,-0.02467148,-0.06826525,-0.10770371,-0.01039421,0.00630727,-0.06026046,-0.03725476,-0.01587424,-0.00222071,-0.01994382,0.09570704,-0.00720743,0.00704012,-0.04848605,-0.03502513,0.06014303,-0.00069485,-0.00225765,0.02182542,-0.04860086],"last_embed":{"tokens":454,"hash":"brmiwv"}}},"last_read":{"hash":"brmiwv","at":1779603227027},"class_name":"SmartSource","last_import":{"mtime":1779603224216,"size":2668,"at":1779603226568,"hash":"brmiwv"},"blocks":{"#":[1,3],"##{1}":[1,1],"######2. **Genetic Algorithm** → Core optimization technique inspired by natural evolution":[4,4],"######3. **Population Generation** → Created multiple possible scheduling solutions":[5,5],"######4. **Fitness Function** → Measured how efficient each schedule was":[6,6],"######5. **Selection** → Chose the best-performing schedules":[7,7],"######6. **Crossover** → Combined two good schedules to create better ones":[8,8],"######7. **Mutation** → Randomly modified schedules to explore new possibilities":[9,9],"######8. **Makespan Optimization** → Reduced total completion time across CPUs":[10,10],"######9. **Multi-CPU Scheduling** → Distributed jobs between multiple processors":[11,11],"######10. **Randomized Job Generation** → Simulated real-world workloads":[12,12],"######11. **Object-Oriented Programming (OOP)** → Used classes like `Job` for structure":[13,13],"######12. **Flask** → Built the backend web application":[14,14],"######13. **HTML Forms** → Took user input from the browser":[15,15],"######14. **CSS Styling** → Designed a modern dashboard UI":[16,16],"######15. **Matplotlib** → Generated performance graphs and analytics":[17,17],"######16. **CPU Load Visualization** → Dis